    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 {className: a4; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: 48px;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">Меросхўрнинг мерос улушидан воз кечиш ҳақидаги аризаси</span></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 318.1163434903px;\">\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ариза келиб тушди: </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#15}Ариза келиб тушган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йил</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 318.18282548476px;\">\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Ариза киритилаётган нотариал идора манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">даги </span><span class=\"structures structure-25\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#25}хусусий амалиёт билан шуғулланувчи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> нотариус </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га </span><span class=\"structures structure-26\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic; display: none;\">{#26}(</span><span class=\"structures structure-26 structure-27\" style=\"className:26 27; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic; display: none;\">{#26}давлат нотариал идорасининг рақами</span><span class=\"structures structure-26\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic; display: none;\">{#26}-сон давлат нотариал идорасига)</span></p>\n<p></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\" width: 318.1163434903px;\">\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Мерос иши № </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#16}Мерос ишининг рақами</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\" width: 318.18282548476px;\">\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#7}Аризачининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#10}Аризачининг рўйхатдан ўтилган уй рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-уйда пропискада турувчи </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#11}Аризачининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">дан </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">(паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">{#12}Аризачининг паспорт серия рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">{#13}Аризачига паспорт берилган худуд</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\"> томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">{#14}Аризачига паспорт берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\"> йилда берилган</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">А<span class=\"leading\"></span>Р И З А</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#18}Ариза берувчининг яшаш манзили </span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#20}Ариза берилаётган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> куни</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Мен – </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#11}Аризачининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#21}Аризачининг вафот этган санаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> куни вафот этган </span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#22}Вафот этган шахснинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">дан қолган мерос мол-мулкнинг ўзимга тегишли бўлган улушимдан акам </span><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#23}Мерос олувчининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> фойдасига воз кечаман. </span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Келгусида мерос мол-мулкига нисбатан ҳеч кимга ҳеч қандай моддий ва мулкий даъво қилмайман.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Аризанинг матнини тўлиқ ўқиб чиқдим, унинг мазмуни ва моҳияти, ҳуқуқий оқибатлари, Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик кодексининг 1147-моддасига асосан меросдан воз кечиш кейинчалик бекор қилиниши ёки қайтариб олиниши мумкин эмаслиги менга нотариус томонидан тушунтирилди ва тушунарли, аризанинг мазмуни менинг асл хоҳиш-истакларимга мос келади.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#11}Аризачининг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>Имзо ______</span>_____________</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Нотариуснинг тасдиқлов ёзуви</span></p>\n</div></div>",
